    "patch_code": "public int hashCode() {\n    int result = 0;\n    Sibling sibling = next;\n    while (sibling != null) {\n        sibling = sibling.next();\n        result++;\n    }\n    Node n = this;\n    while ((n = n.parent) != null) {\n        result++;\n    }\n    \n    Set<Attribute> attrsSet = attrs.asDynamicElement().attributes();\n    Attribute attribute;\n    Iterator iterator = attrsSet.iterator();\n    while (iterator.hasNext()) {\n        attribute = (Attribute) iterator.next();\n        result += attribute.getKey().length() + attribute.getValue().length();\n    }\n    \n    return result; \n}",
